Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveActor Kenneth Aguba whom a Port Harcourt-based just picked up from the street has gotten his life transformed, and his desire elevated.
He now wants a virgin.
Aguba disclosed this during a chat with Pastor Chibuzor Gift Chinyere.
After rescuing the actor bumming about in Egu, Chinyere The cleric on July 5, relocated Aguba to Port-Harcourt, and gave the actor accommodation, Chinyer asked Aguba his desires.
Following the public notice by the pastor, listing the conditions of marriage to the actor, a number of ladies have been signifying interest but the actor insists on marrying a virgin from Israel.
In a viral video, the cleric speaking to his wife and few people around opened up on what Aguba told him about his choice of wife.
“What he told me is that, he wants to marry a virgin,” Chinyere said.
“No only that, Israel I will marry. Israel I will marry. I won’t marry …..” Aguba himself respond
